  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Effect of AVE0657 on Obstructive Sleep Apnea</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Study of the Safety and Activity of Four Escalating Single Doses of AVE0657 in Patients Suffering From Obstructive Sleep Apnea Hypopnea Syndrome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
