  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to assess the activity of 4 escalating doses of
      AVE0657 in comparison to placebo in patients with Obstructive Sleep Apnea Hypopnea Syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
